@host = http://localhost:5000

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

### Create order
POST {{host}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Rivka",
  "amount": 125.50
}

### Replace ORDER_ID with the id from create response
GET {{host}}/orders/ORDER_ID

### Current baseline incorrectly allows Created -> Shipped
PATCH {{host}}/orders/ORDER_ID/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Shipped"
}
